data.description: The Hunter - Beautiful 5 bedroom/4 bath two story home with a welcoming wrap around porch. Bright entry leads to the dining and open concept living area.  Chef’s kitchen with gourmet serving bar opens to the large family room with gas fireplace. Bed and full bath on the main level perfect for guests. Upstairs, Owner’s retreat features a tray ceiling, double vanity bath, separate tub and shower plus a lavish walk-in closet.  The upper level has 2 additional bedrooms with a jack&jill bath and a 3rd secondary bedroom with its own bathroom. Available for move in in March.
